    <id>https://community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam-blog-posts/sap-codejam-hana-ml-in-portugal-2024-09-recap/ba-p/13892209</id>
    <title>SAP CodeJam HANA ML in Portugal 2024-09 Recap</title>
    <updated>2024-10-08T11:59:44.498000+02:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Vitaliy-R</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/183</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;At the end of September, we held two SAP CodeJam events in Portugal: in Lisbon and Porto. The events focused on getting started with Machine Learning using SAP HANA and Python.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="IMG_4701_w.jpeg" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/176858i18E894319A62F82A/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="IMG_4701_w.jpeg" alt="IMG_4701_w.jpeg" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Events where opened by organizers:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/256541"&gt;@jaimecordeiro&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;in Lisbon, and&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/140615"&gt;@MRobalinho&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;in Porto.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="IMG_4875_w.jpeg" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/176866i2124B9C411E29409/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="IMG_4875_w.jpeg" alt="IMG_4875_w.jpeg" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;SAP CodeJam in Porto was the day before the very first SAP Inside Track there, so it was great to share a drink during a Stammtisch after the CodeJam...&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="IMG_4892_w.jpeg" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/176868i70B8AC341463B527/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="IMG_4892_w.jpeg" alt="IMG_4892_w.jpeg" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;...and to present SAP HANA multi-model capabilities at SIT.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="IMG_4914_w.jpeg" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/176880i828E78C68B7AAB3B/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="IMG_4914_w.jpeg" alt="IMG_4914_w.jpeg" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;In the meantime&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/172418"&gt;@marco_v_santos&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;discussed SAP Community with participants.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="IMG_4937.jpeg" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/176882iF087D791DFB09573/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="IMG_4937.jpeg" alt="IMG_4937.jpeg" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;I always take the opportunity to experience at least a little bit of the city I am in, so you can see my photos:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Lisbon:&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DAW1Gm1sl7d/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;https://www.instagram.com/p/DAW1Gm1sl7d/&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Porto and Vila Nova de Gaia:&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DAeULr2ML3C/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;https://www.instagram.com/p/DAeULr2ML3C/&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;P&gt;Now, the next stop is in Wrocław on October 30th.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Would you like to host such an SAP CodeJam? Here are the details:&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-blogs-by-sap/quot-getting-started-with-machine-learning-using-sap-hana-quot-as-a-new-sap/ba-p/13574098" target="_blank"&gt;https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-blogs-by-sap/quot-getting-started-with-machine-learning-using-sap-hana-quot-as-a-new-sap/ba-p/13574098&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam-blog-posts/sap-codejam-hana-ml-in-portugal-2024-09-recap/ba-p/13892209"/>
    <published>2024-10-08T11:59:44.498000+02:00</published>
  </entry>
