  <entry>
    <id>https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-blogs-by-sap/sap-hana-cloud-sessions-at-devtoberfest-2024/ba-p/13921322</id>
    <title>SAP HANA Cloud sessions at Devtoberfest 2024</title>
    <updated>2024-10-28T15:37:22.785000+01:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Vitaliy-R</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/183</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;H1 id="toc-hId-944681886"&gt;Hello SAP HANA Enthusiasts!&lt;/H1&gt;&lt;P&gt;Devtoberfest 2024 has concluded, and we hope you were able to join some of the sessions. If you missed any, no worries! Here is an overview of the SAP HANA Cloud sessions for your convenience.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":blue_circle:"&gt;🔵&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;A href="https://community.sap.com/t5/devtoberfest/embed-the-latest-from-sap-hana-s-ai-functions-into-your-sap-btp-application/ev-p/13873455" target="_blank"&gt;Embed the latest from SAP HANA’s AI functions into your SAP BTP Application&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;with&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/14106"&gt;@ChristophMorgen&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;In this session, Christoph introduced newly added Machine Learning and AI functions designed to enhance your SAP BTP Intelligent Data Applications.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;The features include data-parallel AutoML (such as segmented AutoML TimeSeries), functions for vector data analysis, multi-label classification and regression, and more from the latest SAP HANA Cloud releases, as well as the Predictive Analysis Library (PAL) and the Machine Learning client for SAP HANA.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":blue_circle:"&gt;🔵&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;A href="https://community.sap.com/t5/devtoberfest/sap-hana-cloud-multi-model/ev-p/13862814" target="_blank"&gt;SAP HANA Cloud Multi-Model&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/STRONG&gt;with&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/17350"&gt;@mfath&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;In this session, Markus focused on the Multi-Model capabilities of SAP HANA Cloud, with a particular emphasis on the vector and graph engines. Discover how a robust and scalable data management platform accelerates AI projects through rapid data processing, real-time analytics, and advanced algorithms.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":blue_circle:"&gt;🔵&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;A href="https://community.sap.com/t5/devtoberfest/advanced-strategies-for-intelligent-data-applications-on-sap-hana-cloud/ev-p/13862880" target="_blank"&gt;Advanced Strategies for Intelligent Data Applications on SAP HANA Cloud&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;with &lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/44889"&gt;@VolkerSaggau&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/44579"&gt;@shraddhashetty&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;and &lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/161666"&gt;@breglerj&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;This session explored advanced features of HDI and HANA Tooling. Learn from Jonathan, Volker, and Shraddha about optimizing deployment with HDI parameters, utilizing the Fabric Virtual Table in HDI, and leveraging advanced HANA tooling features, including AI-generated SQL and CDS.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;H2 id="toc-hId-877251100"&gt;Are you new to Devtoberfest?&lt;/H2&gt;&lt;P&gt;Check more about the event at&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://community.sap.com/t5/devtoberfest-blog-posts/devtoberfest-2024-welcome/ba-p/9358" target="_blank"&gt;https://community.sap.com/t5/devtoberfest-blog-posts/devtoberfest-2024-welcome/ba-p/9358&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;by&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/139"&gt;@thomas_jung&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;H2 id="toc-hId-680737595"&gt;Are you looking for sessions from previous editions?&lt;/H2&gt;&lt;P&gt;Please check the&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;A href="https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-blogs-by-sap/data-amp-amp-analytics-sessions-at-devtoberfest-2023/ba-p/13578630" target="_blank"&gt;Data &amp;amp;&amp;amp; Analytics sessions at Devtoberfest 2023&lt;/A&gt;.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;H2 id="toc-hId-484224090"&gt;Enjoy your Devtoberfest 2024 experience!&lt;/H2&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="promo-video-kasimir-square-reduced.gif" style="width: 540px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/184290i2961418DA76A81FE/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="promo-video-kasimir-square-reduced.gif" alt="promo-video-kasimir-square-reduced.gif" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;--Vitaliy&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-blogs-by-sap/sap-hana-cloud-sessions-at-devtoberfest-2024/ba-p/13921322"/>
    <published>2024-10-28T15:37:22.785000+01:00</published>
  </entry>
